snippet.title: Hallways of Fear - Official Trailer | English
snippet.description:
Hallways of Fear is a horror game, focused on jumpscare where you have to find all the innocent souls that are trapped in Abyss without the creatures that inhabit it find you.

The game is in its fifth version

Download for free at: 
https://studiofg934.itch.io/hallways-of-fear
